data.description: New roof in 2019! New garage door 2018! Nestled just off Burnham Avenue, you will find this tree lined mature neighborhood, with well maintained homes and a peaceful environment. This 3 bedroom 2 bath tri-level home was a complete rehab in 2018 and was recently refreshed again (2022) with new carpet, interior paint, new basement flooring and more. Working with experienced SS attorney.
